Learning reflection

  • From Module 1 Creating HTML by combining modern technologies, the most important technique is to understand how R code reflects HTML file and is designed to be portable independent. Also, we need to understand between HTML and markdown files. Those are similar text files but the syntax to indicate is totally different. Markdown should be displayed links or images. In addition, a Markdown processor converts the Markdown code to HTML code. In order to apply data technologies widely, we need to explore a programming language that can be cooperated with data. Also, we need to be more familiar with R programming for data analysis rather than using excel or tabular data.
